---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <section class="py-16 px-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 text-sm">
      This policy outlines how we collect, store, and protect your data when you use SMBCyberHub’s website or digital products.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2 text-gray-800">1. What We Collect</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-2">
      <li>Email address — only when voluntarily submitted to download a free kit or make a purchase.</li>
      <li>Purchase details (via Gumroad) — securely processed off-site through Gumroad’s payment system.</li>
      <li>We do not collect names, addresses, passwords, or behavioral analytics.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2 text-gray-800">2. How We Use Your Data</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-2">
      <li>To deliver downloadable products and provide email-based support.</li>
      <li>To notify you of critical updates or improvements to kits (max 4–6 emails/year).</li>
      <li>We do not use your data for tracking, profiling, or targeted advertising.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2 text-gray-800">3. Data Retention & Deletion</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-2">
      You may request deletion of your email or any record associated with a download at any time by contacting us at info@smbcyberhub.com. We respect your right to be forgotten.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2 text-gray-800">4. Hosting & Compliance</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-2">
      <li>Our site is hosted on Netlify, a GDPR-compliant platform.</li>
      <li>We use Buttondown for email delivery, which adheres to modern privacy standards.</li>
      <li>No third-party analytics (Google, Facebook, etc.) are embedded on our site.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2 text-gray-800">5. Questions?</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
      Contact us at <a href="mailto:info@smbcyberhub.com" class="text-emerald-600 underline">info@smbcyberhub.com</a> if you have questions about privacy or data usage.
    </p>

    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-10">
      Last updated: July 2025 • SMBCyberHub.com
    </p>

    <hr class="my-8" />

    <!-- Internal Legal Links for SEO/orphan fix -->
    <nav class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-6 text-center">
      <a href="/licensing/" class="hover:underline">Licensing</a> &nbsp;|&nbsp;
      <a href="/terms/" class="hover:underline">Terms of Use</a>
    </nav>
  </section>
</Layout>


